<!doctype html>
<html>
  <body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f6f7f9;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f6f7f9;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding:24px;">
          <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
                 style="width:600px;max-width:100%;background:#ffffff;border-radius:8px;
                        padding:24px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,'Apple Color Emoji','Segoe UI Emoji';color:#111827;">
            <tr><td>
              <p style="margin:0 0 12px;">Hi {{ member_name }},</p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 12px;">
                This Saturday, we’ll be hiking <strong>{{ hike_trail_name }}</strong> in <strong>{{ hike_town_name }}</strong>.
                The route is approximately <strong>{{ hike_length_mi }}</strong> miles and should take about
                <strong>{{ hike_estimated_time_hr }}</strong> hours to complete. This hike is classified as
                <strong>{{ hike_difficulty }}</strong>.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 12px;">
                <strong>Important:</strong> Please bring enough water. A good rule of thumb is
                ~1 liter every 2 hours. For this hike, we recommend bringing
                <strong>{{ num_liters }}</strong>
                {% if num_liters == 1 %}liter{% else %}liters{% endif %}.
                We will check that you have water with you. If you do not, we’ll ask you to purchase some (e.g., at Target),
                or you may not be allowed to join for safety reasons (heat/dehydration).
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 12px;">
                We prioritize based on attendance at the last two hikes: members who haven’t attended either get priority,
                followed by those who attended one, then those who attended both. After that, we consider submission time
                (first come, first serve). Drivers are highly appreciated, guaranteed a spot, and entered into an
                end-of-quarter raffle!
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 12px;">
                We aim to alternate between <em>easy/moderate</em> and <em>moderate/difficult</em> weekends so you know what to expect.
                Avid hikers can look forward to more challenging hikes every other weekend, with easier ones in between.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 20px;">
                You can find more details and <strong>sign up</strong> using your personal link below.
                You can use this link to sign up, as well as make edits to or cancel your signup status for this hike before the cutoff time.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 20px;">
                <a href="{{ magic_url }}"
                   style="display:inline-block;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:6px;
                          background:#1d4ed8;color:#ffffff;font-weight:600;">Sign Up</a>
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 12px;">
                The link will expire at the cutoff time of <strong>Thursday at 11:59 PM</strong>. If you’re selected, you’ll receive a confirmation email
                on Friday night with a waiver to sign and submit electronically before Saturday morning.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 16px;">
                If you have any questions, please let us know!
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 4px;">Best,</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 16px;">Hiking Club at UCI Officers</p>

              <!-- Contact block -->
              <div style="background:#1f2937;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;color:#e5e7eb;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,'Apple Color Emoji','Segoe UI Emoji';line-height:1.5;">
                <div style="font-weight:700;color:#facc15;margin-bottom:8px;">Hiking Club at UCI Officers</div>

                <div style="margin:0 0 6px;">
                  Official UCI Campus Page:
                  <a href="https://campusorgs.uci.edu" style="color:#60a5fa;text-decoration:underline;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    Hiking Club at UCI Campus Orgs
                  </a>
                </div>

                <div style="margin:0 0 6px;">
                  Email:
                  <a href="mailto:hikingclub@uci.edu" style="color:#60a5fa;text-decoration:underline;">
                    hikingclub@uci.edu
                  </a>
                </div>

                <div style="margin:0 0 6px;">
                  Linktree:
                  <a href="https://linktr.ee/hikingclubatuci" style="color:#60a5fa;text-decoration:underline;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    linktr.ee/hikingclubatuci
                  </a>
                </div>

                <div style="margin:0 0 6px;">
                  Instagram:
                  <a href="https://instagram.com/hikingclubatirvine" style="color:#60a5fa;text-decoration:underline;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    @hikingclubatirvine
                  </a>
                </div>

                <div style="margin:0;">
                  Discord:
                  <a href="https://discord.gg/tGwU6HeBYv" style="color:#60a5fa;text-decoration:underline;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    discord.gg/tGwU6HeBYv
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </td></tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>